data.description:
"Welcome to your stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with 1509 sq. ft. of living space! This beautiful property boasts a luxurious in-ground pool with a soothing waterfall, perfect for relaxing and entertaining on those hot summer days. The newer roof ensures peace of mind and the covered back patio is ideal for outdoor gatherings with family and friends. Located in a highly sought-after area, this home is perfectly situated near shopping, dining, and top-rated schools. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own your dream home!"
